<package>
  <name>solr</name>
  <summary>The Apache Solr extension is an extremely fast, light-weight, feature-rich library that allows PHP developers to communicate easily and efficiently with Apache Solr server instances using an object-oriented API.</summary>
  <description>It effectively simplifies the process of interacting with Apache Solr using PHP.</description>
